title: I Was Reincarnated and Became a High Elf, but I Got Tired of the Slow Life After 120 Years - Novel Updates
genre: Adventure   Comedy   Fantasy   Slice of Life
tags: Adapted to Manga   Adopted Children   Blacksmith   Carefree Protagonist   Dwarfs   Easy Going Life   Elves   Immortals   Magic   Male Protagonist   Reincarnated in Another World   Reincarnation   Spirits   Student-Teacher Relationship   Sword Wielder   Teachers
author: らる鳥
description:
150 years of life after being reborn as a high elf, who I thought only existed on fiction.

It took 30 years to realize that I had been reborn, and after 120 years of just munching on berries and taking it easy, I finally decided to head into the outside world.

This is the story of an ambiguous existence with a lifespan of over 1000 years — a restless high elf living leisurely as a human.>
